OL,3,CA divide in power: How Grenfell
OL,4,Cexposed Britain's social housing crisis
OL,6,FThe final Grenfell Tower inquiry has
OL,7,Ffound that time and time again,
OL,8,Ftenants were ignored, dismissed and in
OL,9,Fsome cases belittled, ITV News
OL,10,FInvestigations Editor Daniel Hewitt
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FThis is about power - those who have
OL,14,Fit and those who don't.
OL,16,FThose who are given the benefit of the
OL,17,Fdoubt and those who are ignored.
OL,19,FThose believed and those not.
