OL,3,CA divide in power: How Grenfell
OL,4,Cexposed Britain's social housing crisis
OL,6,FGrenfell is the greatest housing
OL,7,Ftragedy in modern British history.
OL,9,FPeople died in a tower block in the
OL,10,Ffifth richest country in the world, in
OL,11,Fits capital city dripping with wealth.
OL,13,FThe deeply uncomfortable truth is
OL,14,Fpeople with power did not do enough to
OL,15,Fstop it from happening for years,
OL,16,Fmultiple times. Call it missed
OL,17,Fopportunity, call it oversight, call
OL,18,Fit complicated, call it neglect.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
