OL,3,CA divide in power: How Grenfell
OL,4,Cexposed Britain's social housing crisis
OL,6,FWho cared enough to listen to social
OL,7,Fhousing tenants when they reported
OL,8,Fproblems over and over and over?
OL,10,FWho cared enough to make sure the
OL,11,Fmaterial being used to house them
OL,12,Fwouldn't kill them?
OL,14,FWho bothered to ensure those who
OL,15,Fsurvived were treated with dignity in
OL,16,Fproper housing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
