OL,3,CA divide in power: How Grenfell
OL,4,Cexposed Britain's social housing crisis
OL,6,FThose who died, those who survived,
OL,7,Fwere overwhelmingly working-class,
OL,8,Foverwhelmingly from ethnic minority
OL,9,Fbackgrounds. Lawyers for the survivors
OL,10,Fcalled race the "elephant in the room".
OL,12,FSeven years. Do we live in a post-
OL,13,FGrenfell Britain? Was it a moment
OL,14,Fwhere everything changed? Was it a
OL,15,Fturning point?
