OL,3,CA divide in power: How Grenfell
OL,4,Cexposed Britain's social housing crisis
OL,6,FLeory McNally, a social housing tenant
OL,7,Fwho had complained time and time again
OL,8,Fabout his unsafe flat, said to me:
OL,9,F"When I used to ring up before, I'd
OL,10,Fsay 'my name's Leroy, Leroy McNally'
OL,11,Fand I got a feeling that puts them on
OL,12,Fthe off-foot because straight away
OL,13,Fthey're (thinking) 'Leroy - black
OL,14,Fperson, we don't want to deal with
OL,15,Fthis person'.
OL,17,F"Eventually I started saying my name
OL,18,Fis Mr McNally - I wouldn't say Leroy -
OL,19,Fand I got a better response."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
