OL,3,CA divide in power: How Grenfell
OL,4,Cexposed Britain's social housing crisis
OL,6,FWe said never again, but again and
OL,7,Fagain and again social housing tenants
OL,8,Fhave been ignored and dismissed by
OL,9,Fcouncils and housing associations
OL,10,Facross the country.
OL,12,FTower blocks still burn. Dangerous
OL,13,Fcladding remains on buildings. Tenants
OL,14,Fstill live in unlivable homes.
OL,16,FWho will be held accountable? And
OL,17,Fwhen? Any prosecutions that would
OL,18,Flikely come a decade or more after the
OL,19,Fdisaster is justice delayed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
