OL,3,CA divide in power: How Grenfell
OL,4,Cexposed Britain's social housing crisis
OL,6,FPeople who survived the fire have died
OL,7,Fwaiting for today's report. It's been
OL,8,Fan intolerably long wait to be told -
OL,9,Fultimately - what people in the tower
OL,10,Fknew to be true all along: that their
OL,11,Fbuilding was not safe, people in
OL,12,Fcharge did not act and did not listen,
OL,13,Fpeople died, and they should all have
OL,14,Flived.
